#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:1
msgid "Decision Matrix"
msgstr "Decision Matrix"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:3
msgid ""
"A rule-based prescription engine that classifies every (island, product) "
"deficit into one of five categories and explains why."
msgstr ""
"島 × 物資の赤字を 5 つのカテゴリに分類し理由を添えて返す rule-based の"
"処方箋エンジン．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:6
msgid "Categories"
msgstr "カテゴリ"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "category"
msgstr "カテゴリ"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "trigger"
msgstr "発火条件"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "suggested action"
msgstr "推奨アクション"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "``increase_production``"
msgstr "``increase_production``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "chronic deficit + high satisfaction + strong route"
msgstr "慢性 deficit + 高満足度 + 強い航路"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "Build more factories of this product."
msgstr "この物資の工場を増やす．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "``trade_flex``"
msgstr "``trade_flex``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "transient deficit + weak correlation + weak route"
msgstr "一過性 deficit + 低相関 + 弱い航路"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "Short-term trading or small route tweak."
msgstr "短期融通 or ルート微調整．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "``rebalance_mix``"
msgstr "``rebalance_mix``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "strong route but still deficit"
msgstr "強い航路があるのに deficit 残存"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "Rewrite the route's loadout, don't add ships."
msgstr "船を増やさず積載構成を見直す．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "``ok``"
msgstr "``ok``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "surplus"
msgstr "黒字"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "Nothing to do."
msgstr "対応不要．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "``monitor``"
msgstr "``monitor``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "rule didn't fire"
msgstr "rule 適用外"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md
msgid "Keep an eye on it."
msgstr "継続観察推奨．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:16
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使い方"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:31
msgid "Tuning thresholds"
msgstr "閾値チューニング"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:33
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"All rule thresholds live in "
"{class}`~anno_save_analyzer.analysis.prescribe.Thresholds`."
msgstr ""
"全閾値は {class}`~anno_save_analyzer.analysis.prescribe.Thresholds` で管理．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:45
msgid ""
"The ``rationale`` column is human-readable; filter on it to audit the "
"rule chain."
msgstr ""
"``rationale`` 列は人間可読．フィルタして rule chain の判定根拠を確認できる．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:48
msgid "What the rules look like"
msgstr "rule の中身"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:50
msgid ""
"**Rule 1** — `persistence == \"chronic\"` ∧ `saturation >= "
"high_saturation` ∧ `(city_name, product) ∈ strong_pairs`  →  "
"``increase_production``"
msgstr ""
"**Rule 1** — `persistence == \"chronic\"` ∧ `saturation >= "
"high_saturation` ∧ `(city_name, product) ∈ strong_pairs`  →  "
"``increase_production``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:52
msgid ""
"**Rule 2** — `persistence == \"transient\"` ∧ `|correlation| < "
"low_correlation` ∧ *not* in strong_pairs  →  ``trade_flex``"
msgstr ""
"**Rule 2** — `persistence == \"transient\"` ∧ `|correlation| < "
"low_correlation` ∧ strong_pairs に *含まれない*  →  ``trade_flex``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:54
msgid "**Rule 3** — strong_pairs ∧ `delta < 0`  →  ``rebalance_mix``"
msgstr "**Rule 3** — strong_pairs ∧ `delta < 0`  →  ``rebalance_mix``"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:55
msgid "**Fallback** — anything else unfinished → ``monitor``."
msgstr "**フォールバック** — 上記に当てはまらないケース → ``monitor``．"

#: ../../source/guide/decision-matrix.md:57
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Persistence, correlation, and strong-pair computation are all pure "
"functions defined in the respective analyzer modules — see "
"{func}`~anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit` and "
"{func}`~anno_save_analyzer.analysis.correlation.saturation_vs_deficit`."
msgstr ""
"持続性・相関・強い pair の計算はすべて各 analyzer モジュールの純関数として"
"実装されています．詳細は "
"{func}`~anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit` と "
"{func}`~anno_save_analyzer.analysis.correlation.saturation_vs_deficit` を参照．"

